content: Data import from Google Workspace to {{organizationName}} {{productName}} is complete!

comment.text: This translation key is used for a completion message when data import from Google Workspace is finished. The message informs users that the import process has been completed successfully and displays the product name of the {{organizationName}}. It appears in a dialog or notification after a successful import operation.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word "Входирането" is not the most natural way to say 'import' in Bulgarian. It's technically correct but sounds awkward and less common.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Импортирането на данни от Google Workspace към {{organizationName}} {{productName}} приключи!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'Η εισαγωγή δεδομένων από το Google Workspace στο {{productName}} του {{organizationName}} ολοκληρώθηκε!' is slightly awkward. A more natural phrasing would be 'Η εισαγωγή δεδομένων από το Google Workspace στο {{productName}} {{organizationName}} έχει ολοκληρωθεί!' or 'Η εισαγωγή δεδομένων από το Google Workspace στο {{productName}} της {{organizationName}} ολοκληρώθηκε!'
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Η εισαγωγή δεδομένων από το Google Workspace στο {{productName}} {{organizationName}} έχει ολοκληρωθεί!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The possessive particle 'του' suggests that {{productName}} belongs to {{organizationName}}. While not incorrect, depending on the specific product relationship, using 'της' (of) might be more appropriate or removing the particle altogether could improve flow.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Η εισαγωγή δεδομένων από το Google Workspace στο {{productName}} της {{organizationName}} ολοκληρώθηκε!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The colon and space after 'productName' in the Finnish translation are not ideal for a user-facing message. It breaks the flow.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Tietojen tuonti Google Workspacesta {{organizationName}} {{productName}} on suoritettu!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase "Data import from Google Workspace" should be translated more naturally in Armenian. A more idiomatic translation would be something like "Google Workspace-ից տվյալներ ներմուծվել են..."
The Armenian translation does not include the spaces before and after the `{{organizationName}}` and `{{productName}}` variables as present in the English.
The Portuguese translation uses 'A importação' which is grammatically correct but sounds slightly less natural than 'A importação de'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: A importação de dados do Google Workspace para o {{organizationName}} {{productName}} foi concluída!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase 'A importação de dados...' should be 'A importação dos dados...' to agree in number with 'dados' (data).
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: A importação dos dados do Google Workspace para o {{organizationName}} {{productName}} foi concluída!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'date' is used incorrectly. 'Date' means 'date' in Romanian, but in this context, 'import' should be the correct translation.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Importul de date din Google Workspace în {{organizationName}} {{productName}} este finalizat!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation uses Cyrillic script which is appropriate for Serbian. However, consistency in handling variables {{organizationName}} and {{productName}} should be ensured across all translations.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Ensure the placeholders {{organizationName}} and {{productName}} are handled consistently in all languages and localization processes.
